<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/58922740">你怎么看待《混血儿亲身经历告诉你，嫁个白人是悲剧》？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="78090199"
data-atoken="264116090"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1511385982"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/58922740/answer/264116090">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="78090199">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="264116090">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-78090199"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>546</a>
</div>

