<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/29635095">跟外国人打架是怎样一种体验？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="118179431"
data-atoken="484603777"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1535965950"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/29635095/answer/484603777">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="118179431">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="484603777">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-118179431"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>269</a>
</div>

