<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/270392402">美国普通人一个月 3000 美元的工资，为什么还会觉得 iPhone X 贵？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="94956186"
data-atoken="356924720"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1522676964"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/270392402/answer/356924720">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="94956186">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="356924720">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-94956186"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>2782</a>
