<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/270392402">美国普通人一个月 3000 美元的工资，为什么还会觉得 iPhone X 贵？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="94831096"
data-atoken="356237934"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1522611620"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/270392402/answer/356237934">
